metadata.name: Towards the dream
metadata.description:
"I finally decided on this adventure. I collected all my brushes and paints and now I'm ready to travel around the world in search of new places and people. The job of an artist is not easy. I chose this to find my path and inspiration. I want to find something more, my purpose and meaning in life, something that will get me out of bed every day and go out into the world. I'm a little excited, so let's walk this road together."

Digital work done by hand in Procreate.
